Package: chan-desktop
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: systemd, xdg-utils
Provides: chan
Conflicts: chan
Replaces: chan
Description: Desktop edition of the chan AI-native IDE
 chan-desktop is the native desktop shell for chan, the AI-native IDE
 for the modern engineer. It embeds the chan server and web app in a
 WebKitGTK window and doubles as the chan/cs command line: invoked as
 chan or cs it dispatches the CLI before any GUI init, so this package
 conflicts with the standalone chan package and provides /usr/bin/chan
 and /usr/bin/cs itself.
